<div class="call-to-action">
<p>The press office can’t help with general enquiries from members of the public either by phone or email.</p>
</div>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/contact-the-dvla">Contact DVLA</a> if you’re a member of the public with a query about your <a href="https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving">driving licence or vehicle</a>.</p>

