<p>Contact the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/driver-and-vehicle-standards-agency/about/media-enquiries">DVSA press office</a> if you have a media query about driver and vehicle standards in Great Britain.</p>

<h2 id="resources-for-the-media">Resources for the media</h2>

<p>All our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?keywords=&announcement_type_option=press-releases&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=driver-and-vehicle-licensing-agency&world_locations%5B%5D=all">press releases since June 2010</a> are available.</p>

<p>You can follow us on <a rel="external" href="https://twitter.com/DVLAgovuk">Twitter</a>, like us on <a rel="external" href="https://www.facebook.com/dvlagovuk">Facebook</a>, watch our videos on <a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/user/dvlagov">YouTube</a> and follow us on <a rel="external" href="https://www.instagram.com/dvlagov/">Instagram</a>. We also have a <a rel="external" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/dvlagovuk/">Flickr account</a>.</p>

